<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .comparison {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        .column {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .left {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .china {
            flex: 1;
            background-color: #ffebee;
        }
        .india {
            flex: 1;
            background-color: #e8f5e9;
        }
        h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 1.3em;
        }
        h2.china {
            color: #d32f2f;
        }
        h2.india {
            color: #388e3c;
        }
        ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
        .emoji {
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="comparison">
        <div class="column left">
            <h2>🚨 Problem</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><span class="emoji">👵👴</span> Aging population</li>
                <li><span class="emoji">📉</span> Birth rates</li>
                <li><span class="emoji">💼</span> Workforce impact</li>
                <li><span class="emoji">💰</span> Economy effect</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="column china">
            <h2 class="china">🇨🇳 China</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><span class="emoji">🏥</span> 14% old people (30% by 2035!)</li>
                <li><span class="emoji">👶</span> 1.09 kids/woman (cat ladies have more)</li>
                <li><span class="emoji">⏳</span> One-child policy backfired</li>
                <li><span class="emoji">😩</span> 1 worker = 2 parents + 4 grandparents</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="column india">
            <h2 class="india">🇮🇳 India</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><span class="emoji">🕺</span> Only 7% old people (for now)</li>
                <li><span class="emoji">👶👶</span> 2.0 kids/woman (perfect balance)</li>
                <li><span class="emoji">💃</span> Still making babies (but slowing)</li>
                <li><span class="emoji">🚀</span> Youth power = economic potential</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.9em; color: #666;">
        <p><span class="emoji">🏆</span> <b>Verdict:</b> China = retirement home | India = lit party (for now)</p>
        <p>TL;DR scrolled this far? Go watch cat videos 🐱</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
